      "order_number": 0,
      "text": "Thank you for calling Dramatic Real Estate. Please listen carefully to the following menu options. If you are a homeowner and wish to have nomadic manage or lease your rental property, please press one. If you are a prospective tenant and have questions about touring leasing, or applying to one of our rental properties, please press two. If you are an existing client or tenant and have a question about maintenance issues, please press three. For all other questions please press four, please hold while I get an automatic representative to assist you, please note that all calls may be recorded for quality and training purposes. If you'd like to request a call back, please press two. Good afternoon, real estate sam speaking."
